WEBVTT

00:01.001 --> 00:01.835
Ah-hyuck!

00:02.877 --> 00:04.295
♪ H-h-h-hit it ♪

00:04.379 --> 00:06.464
♪ Like father, like son ♪

00:07.007 --> 00:08.591
♪ You're always number one ♪

00:08.675 --> 00:09.843
[both] Yes!

00:09.926 --> 00:11.177
♪ There's buddies
There's pals ♪

00:11.261 --> 00:12.095
Yeah!

00:12.178 --> 00:14.389
♪ You always seem to work things out ♪

00:14.472 --> 00:16.641
♪ Can't you see you're two of a kind ♪

00:17.058 --> 00:18.685
♪ Lookin' for a real good time ♪

00:18.768 --> 00:19.728
Whoa!

00:19.811 --> 00:21.104
♪ A real good time ♪

00:21.187 --> 00:22.439
Aah!

00:22.522 --> 00:24.024
♪ Report to the Goof Troop ♪

00:24.107 --> 00:26.192
♪ And we'll always stick together ♪

00:26.276 --> 00:27.694
♪ Always stick together ♪

00:27.777 --> 00:29.362
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:29.446 --> 00:31.656
♪ The best of friends forever ♪

00:33.116 --> 00:35.285
♪ Side by side wherever we go ♪

00:35.368 --> 00:39.330
♪ We're always ready to roll ♪

00:39.914 --> 00:41.082
♪ Now gimme a beat ♪

00:41.166 --> 00:42.292
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:42.375 --> 00:44.878
♪ And we always stick together ♪

00:44.961 --> 00:45.962
Gawrsh!

00:46.046 --> 00:47.505
♪ We're the Goof Troop ♪

00:47.589 --> 00:50.258
♪ The best of friends forever ♪

00:51.468 --> 00:53.636
♪ Now we're calling everyone ♪

00:53.720 --> 00:55.305
♪ Come along and join the fun ♪

00:55.347 --> 00:56.931
♪ Report to the Goof Troop ♪

00:57.015 --> 00:58.850
♪ Baa ba doo da bop baa ba doo bop ♪

00:58.933 --> 00:59.851
Yeah!

01:00.185 --> 01:01.102
[indistinct screaming]

01:02.270 --> 01:03.313
[cat yowling]

01:03.730 --> 01:04.814
Aah!

01:04.898 --> 01:06.941
Ha ha ha!

01:10.278 --> 01:13.323
Oh, I wasn't scared. No, sir!

01:13.406 --> 01:15.116
OK, Pistol. Let's go.

01:15.200 --> 01:16.993
Halloween's not very scary.

01:17.077 --> 01:20.997
We gotta get dad. You don't
wanna miss trick or treat, do ya?

01:21.664 --> 01:23.541
Just one more ride, please,
please, pretty please,

01:23.625 --> 01:25.085
please, please, please?

01:25.168 --> 01:27.962
[Pistol] And there was witches,
and spooky green goblins,

01:28.046 --> 01:31.591
and bats and cats,
and put the hecks on me, slimy skeletons.

01:31.675 --> 01:34.552
I'm gonna get 10 pounds of candy,
and Daddy's dressing up just like me.

01:34.636 --> 01:38.098
Yeah. Remember when
we used to get that way?

01:39.140 --> 01:41.685
Get outta my way! Here I come! Whoo-hoo!

01:43.436 --> 01:46.940
Wow. This place looks like a bad dream.

01:47.524 --> 01:50.568
-This is Daddy's new hotel?
-Pretty much.

01:51.111 --> 01:53.321
I've been waitin' 10 minutes for you kids.

01:53.405 --> 01:55.949
Ooh, Daddy, Daddy, Daddy,
this looks like a rattletrap,

01:56.032 --> 01:57.450
not a hotel.

01:57.534 --> 02:00.453
Well, wait'll it's fixed up, Pistolkins.

02:00.537 --> 02:04.040
Pete's bed 'n' breakfast
is gonna be top 10.

02:04.124 --> 02:07.836
Breakfast? Why don't you name
it Pistol's Pancake House.

02:07.919 --> 02:09.879
I think that sounds
like a very, very tasty name.

02:09.963 --> 02:10.964
What do you think?

02:11.047 --> 02:14.134
Oh, well, Punkidoodle,
if Daddy did that...

02:14.217 --> 02:16.928
Hey, Peej,
are you up for a great Halloween

02:17.012 --> 02:18.888
just like old times?

02:18.972 --> 02:21.016
Yeah, I'm in. Like what?

02:21.099 --> 02:25.103
Like, uh, stay up all night in a cemetery
or, or, or see a ghost

02:25.186 --> 02:27.022
or, uh, something.

02:27.105 --> 02:28.231
[crash]

02:28.565 --> 02:30.400
Ghost!

02:33.069 --> 02:34.821
Get offa me, you--

02:34.904 --> 02:37.741
G-g-ghosts, Mr. Pete! Real ghosts!

02:37.824 --> 02:39.367
We seen 'em!

02:39.576 --> 02:40.827
[both] Ghosts!

02:41.119 --> 02:44.330
Scared Lumpy so much,
his voice box froze over.

02:44.414 --> 02:47.375
It was horrible, terrible!

02:47.417 --> 02:50.462
There were footsteps,
and the door slammed,

02:50.545 --> 02:53.798
and the ghosties popped
right up through the floor.

02:53.882 --> 02:55.633
That's all we could take!

02:55.717 --> 02:58.094
Ghosts, my Aunt Fanny.

02:58.178 --> 03:01.139
You two coffee coolers
better get back to work.

03:01.222 --> 03:05.935
I'm tellin' ya there's ghosts,
and I don't want us around!

03:06.019 --> 03:07.437
[both] Wow!

03:07.520 --> 03:11.441
Don't go makin' up stuff about
ghosts hauntin' my hotel.

03:11.524 --> 03:12.859
-[screams]
-But--

03:12.942 --> 03:16.196
But nothin'!
You wanna scare off my customers!

03:16.279 --> 03:17.614
[whistles]

03:17.697 --> 03:20.742
I always knew the old
Spoonerville mansion was haunted.

03:21.409 --> 03:23.411
Yeah! Real ghosts!

03:23.995 --> 03:28.541
Peej, this could be
the Halloween we've been waitin' for.

03:29.959 --> 03:31.920
[wolf howls]

03:35.090 --> 03:37.717
Come on, P.J. Don't you wanna see a ghost?

03:38.218 --> 03:41.221
I-I-I'm not so sure anymore, Maxie.

03:41.304 --> 03:42.847
But this is our chance!

03:43.431 --> 03:47.185
Ooh! My arm's kinda sore.
Maybe I better get home.

03:47.268 --> 03:49.688
Hey, do I detect chicken feathers?

03:49.771 --> 03:51.189
Bawk bawk bawk!

03:51.272 --> 03:54.150
No. I'm not scared. It's just--

03:54.234 --> 03:57.278
Come on, P.J.
This'll be our Halloween to remember.

03:57.362 --> 03:59.280
That's what I'm afraid of.

04:04.244 --> 04:05.870
Aah!

04:05.954 --> 04:07.664
Hey. What if we're arrested
for trespassin'?

04:08.039 --> 04:09.290
Chill out, Peej.

04:09.374 --> 04:11.209
Your dad owns the place.

04:11.292 --> 04:13.420
Ugh. Yucka-booey! Yecchh!

04:13.503 --> 04:15.213
-[creaking open]
-What?

04:17.924 --> 04:19.509
Aah!

04:20.844 --> 04:23.805
-What was that?
-I don't even wanna know.

04:23.888 --> 04:27.726
Well, we're here now.
Let's have a look see.

04:27.809 --> 04:30.645
M-Maybe we shouldn't you
know, because my...

04:30.729 --> 04:33.231
My allergies might act up.

04:33.314 --> 04:36.026
[creaking]

04:37.277 --> 04:41.072
I don't know, it's pretty dusty in here,
not to mention musty.

04:41.239 --> 04:42.741
And then, of course, you know,

04:42.824 --> 04:45.660
there's mildew spores
to contend with, and--

04:47.078 --> 04:49.998
Ha ha ha!

04:56.171 --> 04:57.839
[both] G-g-ghost!

04:57.922 --> 04:59.841
Aah!

05:02.302 --> 05:04.387
-Help! It's got me!
-Oh, no!

05:04.471 --> 05:06.181
Help!

05:06.264 --> 05:07.682
I gotcha, Maxie!

05:07.766 --> 05:09.392
Whoa!

05:10.518 --> 05:12.103
[both] Outta here!

05:14.773 --> 05:16.941
[humming]

05:19.027 --> 05:21.279
A-hyuck! There ya go, punky!

05:23.448 --> 05:24.407
[sniffs]

05:24.491 --> 05:25.408
[meow]

05:25.492 --> 05:26.993
[meow]

05:28.286 --> 05:29.621
[screeches]

05:29.954 --> 05:31.831
[choking]

05:36.002 --> 05:37.295
[meow]

05:38.922 --> 05:40.340
-Dad!
-Mr G!

05:40.757 --> 05:41.925
Aah!

05:42.008 --> 05:44.469
Hey, what's the ruckus, boys?

05:44.552 --> 05:45.929
You look like you've seen a ghost.

05:46.012 --> 05:48.848
We did. Up at the Spoonerville mansion!

05:48.932 --> 05:50.600
-It was blue!
-It floated through the mirror.

05:50.684 --> 05:52.268
Yeah, yeah,
you could see right through it!

05:52.352 --> 05:53.687
Yeah, and it laughed like this. Show him.

05:53.770 --> 05:55.897
Yeah, yeah. "Ooh ha ha!"

05:55.980 --> 05:58.024
A ghost? Gawrsh!

05:58.108 --> 06:00.193
I always wanted to see a real ghost.

06:00.276 --> 06:03.071
P.J., take your sister around the block.

06:03.738 --> 06:07.200
These clodhoppers are killin' my bunions.

06:07.283 --> 06:09.828
Dad, we went up to the Spoonerville place!

06:09.911 --> 06:11.079
We saw the ghost!

06:11.162 --> 06:12.288
A ghost?

06:12.372 --> 06:15.917
Oh, Daddy, we're so lucky.
I really wanna see it!

06:16.001 --> 06:18.211
Can I, Daddy, please, please?
I really would like to see it!

06:18.294 --> 06:20.005
There's no such thing as ghosts.

06:20.088 --> 06:23.550
I'm not sure about that, Petey.

06:23.633 --> 06:26.344
You see this watch? It's haunted!

06:26.803 --> 06:31.725
It was awarded to my great,
great granddaddy Gooferamus T. Goofy

06:31.808 --> 06:33.393
for catchin' ghosts.

06:33.476 --> 06:34.436
[all] Really?

06:34.519 --> 06:37.605
Yep. He cleaned out
a whole ghost town once.

06:38.023 --> 06:40.859
Never could get the darned
thing to work, though.

06:40.942 --> 06:42.610
[Pete] What a bunch of malarkey!

06:43.111 --> 06:46.072
Gooferamus T., ghosts 'n' goblins.

06:46.156 --> 06:47.782
I'm surrounded by sissies!

06:48.491 --> 06:51.077
Get mama will take you
trick or treatin', pumpkin.

06:51.661 --> 06:55.206
I'm gonna take these chicken livers
up to the hotel,

06:55.290 --> 06:59.711
and prove once and for all
there's no such thing as ghosts!

07:01.629 --> 07:04.883
Gawrsh! The place looks haunted to me.

07:05.467 --> 07:07.552
Stifle it, Goof.

07:07.635 --> 07:08.720
Well, it could be.

07:09.012 --> 07:13.850
OK, you jellyfish,
we're gonna put your ghost story to bed.

07:14.476 --> 07:17.854
Uh, why don't you check it out, Dad, OK?

07:17.937 --> 07:19.064
We'll, um...

07:19.147 --> 07:20.398
Stand guard outside.

07:20.607 --> 07:21.858
Good idea.

07:21.941 --> 07:25.820
Me and Goof will give the once over
while you protect us.

07:30.575 --> 07:33.161
Boys said the ghostie was up there.

07:33.578 --> 07:34.871
Snap out of it!

07:34.954 --> 07:37.248
You're as Lily-livered as the kiddies!

07:37.332 --> 07:39.626
[screaming]

07:39.709 --> 07:41.461
Ahem.

07:41.544 --> 07:43.004
Should've shaved this mornin'.

07:44.881 --> 07:47.592
Peej, do you think maybe we overreacted?

07:47.676 --> 07:49.052
Maybe so.

07:50.887 --> 07:52.347
D-D-Did you see that?

07:52.430 --> 07:54.766
I-I-I'm not sure.

07:54.933 --> 07:56.101
Whoo!

07:56.184 --> 07:58.144
[both] Ghosts!

08:01.356 --> 08:03.775
[ghosts] Whoo! Whoo!

08:03.858 --> 08:05.443
[teeth chattering]

08:05.527 --> 08:06.736
Aah!

08:06.820 --> 08:08.780
Music lessons.

08:10.490 --> 08:12.117
Get me outta here!

08:15.787 --> 08:17.414
Aw, don't leave!

08:17.497 --> 08:20.000
We love havin' company.

08:20.083 --> 08:21.960
Yeah, stay for tea!

08:23.753 --> 08:25.213
[both shuddering]

08:30.510 --> 08:33.847
-[coughing]
-[sputtering]

08:34.514 --> 08:35.640
Aah!

08:35.724 --> 08:37.434
Aah!

08:37.517 --> 08:40.228
We gotta save 'em, Peej.

08:40.311 --> 08:41.229
Why?

08:42.480 --> 08:43.481
OK.

08:43.982 --> 08:45.150
[inhales]

08:45.233 --> 08:46.568
[both] Hee-yah!

08:46.651 --> 08:48.987
Ya ha ha ha ha!

08:50.113 --> 08:51.448
[blowing trumpet]

08:52.365 --> 08:54.159
Here, bully, bully, bully.

08:54.242 --> 08:55.410
Outta my way!

08:57.412 --> 08:58.371
Ole!

09:00.957 --> 09:02.334
Aah, aah, aah!

09:02.834 --> 09:05.086
Who turned out the lights?

09:06.713 --> 09:07.547
[screaming]

09:13.386 --> 09:15.055
Uh b-b-b-b-b-b.

09:22.312 --> 09:24.272
Take this, ya ghosties.

09:28.068 --> 09:29.069
Oops!

09:29.152 --> 09:30.278
[both] Dad! Dad!

09:30.737 --> 09:33.406
Ooh! It's the kiddies.

09:36.326 --> 09:38.161
Aah! Yi!

09:38.244 --> 09:39.746
[Max] Boogie, buddy!

09:42.040 --> 09:43.416
Bye-bye. Bye-bye.

09:45.502 --> 09:47.045
Whoa!

09:48.713 --> 09:51.049
Whoa! Waah!

09:54.052 --> 09:55.637
Let's get Moe.

09:56.221 --> 10:00.225
I gotta tell ya, I haven't had so much fun
since I was eight.

10:01.309 --> 10:03.895
I do believe in ghosts!
I do believe in ghosts!

10:03.978 --> 10:06.189
I do, I do, I do believe in ghosts.

10:06.272 --> 10:08.608
Aah! A monster!

10:09.651 --> 10:12.028
-Hang on, Dad!
-We'll get ya down!

10:18.827 --> 10:21.204
-Yaaa! Yi!
-Run for it!

10:21.287 --> 10:25.125
Outta my hotel, ya see-through sapheads!

10:25.208 --> 10:26.167
[clang]

10:27.836 --> 10:29.421
-Oof!
-Ugh!

10:29.504 --> 10:32.465
-Whoa!
-Wh-wh-whoa!

10:32.549 --> 10:34.801
-Whoa ho!
-Hey!

10:34.884 --> 10:36.386
Whoa!

10:37.429 --> 10:39.305
Whoa!

10:41.725 --> 10:43.184
[Goofy] Run fer it, boys!

10:43.727 --> 10:44.769
Aah!

10:44.853 --> 10:46.229
Aah!

10:49.816 --> 10:51.109
P.J., look!

10:59.993 --> 11:01.369
Whoa!

11:10.045 --> 11:12.464
♪ Jingle bells, jingle bells ♪

11:12.547 --> 11:15.300
♪ Jingle all the way ♪

11:15.383 --> 11:18.636
[scat singing]

11:19.888 --> 11:21.723
[both] Dad! Dad!

11:23.141 --> 11:26.895
[Pete] Get outta here, boys. Go get help!

11:28.355 --> 11:29.773
-Mom!
-Mrs. P!

11:31.983 --> 11:33.068
Mrs. P, ghosts!

11:33.151 --> 11:36.154
-Help, Mom!
-Ghosts!

11:37.280 --> 11:38.782
Aw, they're still trick or treatin'.

11:40.575 --> 11:41.409
[both gasp]

11:43.286 --> 11:45.705
Oh ho ho!

11:47.123 --> 11:48.291
Ah-hyuck!

11:48.375 --> 11:50.543
Happy Halloween!

11:50.627 --> 11:52.837
Aah! Aah!

11:56.216 --> 11:57.509
[toot]

11:59.177 --> 12:01.346
[both] Ghosts!

12:01.680 --> 12:03.139
[toot]

12:04.307 --> 12:06.267
Hey, where's the party?

12:06.893 --> 12:09.562
You're a-- y-y-you're a g-g-g--

12:09.646 --> 12:13.149
Ghost. Ah-hyuck!
What'd ya expect on Halloween?

12:14.484 --> 12:17.946
-[tooting]
-[purring]

12:23.785 --> 12:26.913
Wow! This is your watch. Then you're--

12:26.996 --> 12:29.958
Gooferamus T. Goofy at your service.

12:30.500 --> 12:31.960
You're my ancestor?

12:32.335 --> 12:37.549
You betchie. Aren't you a lucky duck?
Inherited the Goofy good looks.

12:38.008 --> 12:41.219
Wow! You're the ghost catcher.

12:41.511 --> 12:45.974
Listen, our dads are trapped by ghosts.
I--I mean real ghosts. You know.

12:46.057 --> 12:47.767
That, uh-- well, that is,
you know, not like you.

12:47.851 --> 12:49.352
And ya need some hints.

12:51.146 --> 12:54.816
Well, my most best trick
was sticky sorghum.

12:54.899 --> 12:55.859
[both] Sorghum?

12:55.942 --> 12:59.195
Or mop 'em up, or use piney tar bubbles.

12:59.279 --> 13:02.365
Almost forgot.
You can suck 'em up with a bellows, too.

13:03.283 --> 13:04.868
A bellows?

13:05.368 --> 13:06.828
What's he talkin' about, man?

13:10.749 --> 13:14.210
Just use your ingenuity,
and you can't go wrong.

13:18.673 --> 13:21.843
Lots of luck, boys.
Gotta get back to the party!

13:22.093 --> 13:23.636
[toots]

13:23.720 --> 13:24.721
Ah-hyuck!

13:29.851 --> 13:31.269
Piney tar?

13:33.355 --> 13:34.814
Ladies and gentlemen,

13:34.898 --> 13:39.444
let's have a hand
for our high-flying daredevils!

13:47.285 --> 13:49.329
Ah-hyuck! This is kind of fun.

13:49.412 --> 13:52.707
Let me down, you stupid blobs of tapioca!

13:58.046 --> 13:59.214
Ooh! Aah!

13:59.422 --> 14:01.216
Oh, don't worry, boys!

14:01.299 --> 14:03.718
We wouldn't let you work without a net.

14:05.720 --> 14:06.888
[both exclaiming]

14:11.184 --> 14:13.812
Hey, another round of applause.

14:20.902 --> 14:23.571
Hey, let's play dress up, huh?

14:24.364 --> 14:27.117
Ha ha hoo! Ha ha ha ha!

14:33.456 --> 14:36.209
[both screaming]

14:36.292 --> 14:39.504
[both] How... embarrassing.

14:39.838 --> 14:42.757
Operation Halloween rescue.

14:43.008 --> 14:44.384
Let's do it!

14:51.933 --> 14:56.146
Uh...j-just one question.
What are we doin', man?

14:56.229 --> 14:58.732
Look, Gooferamus said sorghum.

14:58.815 --> 15:03.028
And we know it's sticky, right?
So, let's use honey.

15:04.320 --> 15:06.156
I'll aim. You spray.

15:06.239 --> 15:11.161
Help! Lemme out!
I never took pianer lessons!

15:11.244 --> 15:12.662
Help!

15:13.455 --> 15:15.081
Old maid!

15:16.583 --> 15:18.293
Wussy card games!

15:18.376 --> 15:21.463
-Hee-yeow! Ya!
-Wa! Whoa!

15:21.546 --> 15:23.214
-Wa!
-Ya!

15:29.554 --> 15:31.723
[mumbling]

15:33.475 --> 15:35.727
-Uh-oh!
-Wrong ghost.

15:37.854 --> 15:38.980
Look!

15:39.064 --> 15:42.650
Hoo ha ha ha! Heh heh heh!

15:43.651 --> 15:45.528
Swab the decks, P.J.!

15:45.612 --> 15:47.655
Gooferamus tip number two.

15:47.739 --> 15:49.949
-Oh!
-Yeow!

15:55.789 --> 15:57.207
Two down!

15:58.083 --> 16:02.587
Whoa whoa whoa aah aah aah!

16:03.338 --> 16:05.965
[slow motion] P...

16:06.049 --> 16:07.926
J...

16:08.802 --> 16:10.178
Not now, Dad.

16:20.522 --> 16:21.523
[bottle shattering]

16:25.026 --> 16:26.319
[all scatting]

16:35.286 --> 16:37.539
Oh, what's next on the hit parade?

16:37.622 --> 16:39.374
Modern-day bellows.

16:39.457 --> 16:42.585
[grunts] Vac-o-rama!

16:47.841 --> 16:49.300
Hold on!

16:55.598 --> 16:57.350
[glug glug glug]

16:57.434 --> 16:59.394
[thump thump thump]

17:07.986 --> 17:10.864
Let's add bubbles,
hit 'em with a double whammy!

17:14.993 --> 17:16.119
[both screaming]

17:40.894 --> 17:43.813
Say "ahh", and you'll get a lollipop.

17:43.897 --> 17:45.357
Grape or cherry?

17:53.698 --> 17:56.034
P.J.? Help!

17:56.117 --> 17:57.494
Hang on, Dad!

18:03.875 --> 18:07.420
Now, get outta my hotel and stay out!

18:11.758 --> 18:15.595
Now boys, we would just
love to make like a tree

18:15.679 --> 18:17.639
and leave this honky-tonk.

18:17.722 --> 18:19.057
Yeah. We're bored.

18:19.349 --> 18:21.226
Been stuck here since '29.

18:21.309 --> 18:23.353
Well, why can't ya leave?

18:25.689 --> 18:27.232
We're musicians, man.

18:27.607 --> 18:29.401
Never got to play our gig.

18:29.484 --> 18:33.822
A load of Halloween corn fermented
and blew up the place!

18:33.905 --> 18:36.157
Perfect. I'll never get rid of 'em.

18:36.241 --> 18:39.494
Hey, wait! What if you got to play now?

18:39.828 --> 18:42.414
Then we could 23 skiddoo!

18:42.497 --> 18:46.001
But we have to be invited
by the owner first.

18:46.084 --> 18:47.961
Invited by the owner fir--

18:48.628 --> 18:50.088
Oh, no!

18:58.763 --> 19:00.557
So, I'm happy to present--

19:00.640 --> 19:03.393
[whispering]

19:03.476 --> 19:04.728
Fingers McFee

19:04.811 --> 19:08.189
and his ragamuffin ragtime band.

19:08.273 --> 19:11.526
[playing ragtime music]

19:11.609 --> 19:14.320
A big hand, ladies and gentlemen.

19:14.404 --> 19:16.281
[cheers and whistles]

19:16.364 --> 19:18.324
Yeah! All right!

19:19.993 --> 19:21.661
[playing ragtime music]

19:30.545 --> 19:31.588
Big whoop.

19:31.671 --> 19:32.881
[blaring]

19:33.798 --> 19:35.884
[blaring]

19:40.138 --> 19:42.390
Ha ha ha. Ha ha. Stop that!

19:42.474 --> 19:45.894
Wow, cool!
Dad doesn't even know chopsticks.

19:51.316 --> 19:53.318
[horns blaring]

19:55.737 --> 19:57.572
[applause]

20:02.494 --> 20:05.205
[drumming]

20:16.383 --> 20:17.509
[music continues]

20:23.056 --> 20:24.599
Aah ho ho!

20:26.184 --> 20:28.186
[cheering, applause]

20:29.020 --> 20:30.105
Ptooey!

20:30.188 --> 20:31.189
[belches]

20:31.272 --> 20:33.900
[laughing]

20:36.569 --> 20:41.908
Oh! Oh, ooh! Oh, Pumpkin Whiskers.
I didn't know you were so talented.

20:41.991 --> 20:45.161
Oh, Dad, can you do it again,
please, please, please?

20:45.245 --> 20:49.124
I want to see it 40 million,
trillion, billions and 18 more times.

20:50.583 --> 20:52.877
[horn honks]

20:53.128 --> 20:57.507
Come on, fellas.
Gotta hit Altoona in two hours.

20:57.674 --> 21:00.343
-See you around.
-Asta la bye-bye.

21:00.427 --> 21:02.512
Want you fellas to have these.

21:02.595 --> 21:04.806
Makes you honorary rascals.

21:04.889 --> 21:06.641
-Wow, cool!
-Thanks!

21:07.142 --> 21:11.062
Shucks, boys, if it weren't for you,

21:11.146 --> 21:13.690
we'd have been stuck in this dive forever.

21:13.815 --> 21:17.235
Come on, Moe. Your fans await.

21:17.318 --> 21:21.489
-Hey, see you later, guys.
-Goodbye, now. Thanks for everything.

21:22.741 --> 21:25.827
[ghosts singing] ♪ Ninety-nine gaggles
of ghosts on the wall ♪

21:25.910 --> 21:28.621
♪ Ninety-nine gaggles of ghosts ♪

21:28.705 --> 21:31.791
♪ You take one down and throw it around ♪

21:31.875 --> 21:34.753
♪ Ninety-eight gaggles of ghosts
on the wall ♪

21:40.884 --> 21:42.719
Hey, Peej.

21:42.802 --> 21:45.597
[both] Best Halloween ever!

21:45.680 --> 21:48.475
Those stupid ghosts... Ghosts...

21:48.558 --> 21:50.477
Aah!

21:50.560 --> 21:52.354
Whoa-whoa-whoa- whoa-whoa-whoa!

21:53.271 --> 21:56.524
Hey, this the haunted hotel
we heard about?

21:56.608 --> 21:58.860
Yes, with ghosts and everything?

21:58.943 --> 22:01.696
No ghosts! K-N-O-W! No!

22:01.780 --> 22:03.948
Nada. Zip. Zero. Zilch. Zippo.

22:04.032 --> 22:06.368
Oh, then we don't want to stay here.

22:07.202 --> 22:10.080
Uh, wait, uh, come back!

22:10.163 --> 22:12.499
Wait a second! We got ghosts!

22:12.582 --> 22:14.042
Whoo whoo!

22:14.376 --> 22:17.671
There's one now!
Was that a ghost? That's a ghost!

22:19.172 --> 22:20.256
♪ Gimme a beat ♪

22:20.340 --> 22:22.342
[theme music playing]

22:47.617 --> 22:48.743
Yeah!
